data.description: Recently cut over large parcel of land with nice stream bordering back end of lot. Also borders snowmobile trail. Build close to road for ease of access and utilities at road, or build several hundred feet back closer to stream. Great location for snowmobile & ATV riding, many fishing and hunting areas close by as well. Waterfrontage is estimated. Power at road.
